Whereas the contractor provides a guarantee of energy savings for the Energy Savings Performance
			 Contract and the utility provides energy savings performance assurances or
			 guarantees of the savings for the Utility Energy Service Contract;

Whereas the Office of Management and Budget first recognized savings from Energy Savings
			 Performance Contracts and Utility Energy Service Contracts on an annual
			 basis throughout the term of the contract as far back as 1998;
